The first example:
•  after the first query a = [2, 1, 3], inversion: (2, 1);
•  after the second query a = [2, 3, 1], inversions: (3, 1), (3, 2).
The second example:
•  a = [1, 2, 4, 3], inversion: (4, 3);
•  a = [3, 4, 2, 1], inversions: (3, 1), (4, 1), (3, 2), (4, 2), (4, 3);
•  a = [1, 2, 4, 3], inversion: (4, 3);
•  a = [1, 4, 2, 3], inversions: (3, 2), (4, 2).
